I"<p>Circa 100 homes remain earmarked for demolition in phase 3 of Peabody’s redevelopment of the St John’s Hill estate near Clapham Junction.</p>

<p>Phases 1 and 2 are underway and demoliton is due to start on the remaining phase in 2021.</p>

<p>The estate was originally designated for redevelopment in Wandsworth’s <a href="https://www.wandsworth.gov.uk/media/1937/sd_021_site_specific_sites_allocations_document__2016_.pdf">2016 Local Plan</a>.</p>

